  section
    h2 adding smelting
    ul
      li Since I have a coin, I want to be able to smelt my coins into gold
      li Your item can be produced by smelting, or an ingredient
      li To add a smelting recipe, simply add the following code to <code>preInit()</code>
        pre
          code(data-trim contenteditable)
            | //Example of smelting
            | ItemStack input = new ItemStack(Items.water_bucket);
            | ItemStack output = new ItemStack(Blocks.obsidian);
            | GameRegistry.addSmelting(input, output, 0.1f);
      li <code>0.1f</code> is how much experience you get for smelting
      li Experience must be between 0 and 1

